<subSubSection id="C347651CFFB2F845FF192733FEAEFE4F" pageId="3" pageNumber="438" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BE23697FFB2F845FF192733FDE6FEF8" blockId="3.[151,1437,151,466]" pageId="3" pageNumber="438">
<emphasis id="B929EA85FFB2F845FF192733FEBFFE81" bold="true" box="[199,338,258,284]" pageId="3" pageNumber="438">Comments:</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="4C5D4D14FFB2F845FE862732FE18FE81" authorityName="Mannerheim" authorityYear="1837" box="[344,501,259,284]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Hiperantha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="438" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="menetriesii">
<emphasis id="B929EA85FFB2F845FE862732FE18FE81" box="[344,501,259,284]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="438">H. menetriesii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was described by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFCC4B66FFB2F845FD1F2732FC4CFE80" author="Mannerheim" box="[705,929,259,285]" firstAuthor="Mannerheim" pageId="3" pageNumber="438" pagination="1 - 126" refId="ref2290" refString="Mannerheim, C. G. von (1837) Enumeration des Buprestides, et description de quelques nouvelles especes de cette tribu de la famille des Sternoxes, de la collection de M. Le Comte Mannerheim. Bulletin de la Societe Imperiale des Naturalistes des Moscou, 8, 1 - 126." type="journal article" year="1837">Mannerheim (1837)</bibRefCitation>
from a single specimen that he received from M. Hummel, who received it from M. Besche, who, in turn, had received it from the collector, M. Ménétriés, to whom the species was dedicated.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BE23697FFB2F845FF19275EFEAEFE4F" blockId="3.[151,1437,151,466]" pageId="3" pageNumber="438">
The original description indicates that the type specimen was collected by M. Ménétriés in “Brasilia; ad Serra da Lapa in provincial 
<collectingRegion id="4999F875FFB2F845FE4627A2FDD7FE30" box="[408,570,403,429]" country="Brazil" name="Minas Gerais" pageId="3" pageNumber="438">Minas Geraïs</collectingRegion>
.”. 
<location id="8E82604CFFB2F845FD8B27A2FD6CFE30" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03F48781FFB3F845FF4921A7FEAEFE4F:8E82604CFFB2F845FD8B27A2FD6CFE30" box="[597,641,403,429]" name="The" pageId="3" pageNumber="438" stateProvince="Minas Gerais">The</location>
<typeStatus id="54E68835FFB2F845FD5427A2FD1CFE30" box="[650,753,403,429]" pageId="3" pageNumber="438">lectotype</typeStatus>
housed at the 
<collectionCode id="ED4CAE52FFB2F845FC4027A2FC01FE30" box="[926,1004,403,429]" pageId="3" pageNumber="438">MZHF</collectionCode>
is labelled as “Brasilia Min. Geraës” (
<collectorName id="26A85341FFB2F845FF412786FEEEFE4C" box="[159,259,439,465]" pageId="3" pageNumber="438">Hummel</collectorName>
leg.).
</paragraph>
